<TITLE>
Nihancan, the Arapaho trickster (Niatha, Nihansan, Nihanca)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Nihancan (Niatha), 
trickster hero of the Arapaho.">
